name: Mr.takealook Princess Style
description:
Trained using specific series of images (44 with duplicates) from Mr.Takealook. I was pretty impressed how it was able to capture the style so well.

I used random saved prompts I've been making to generate the examples. That is to say, I put little effort in the prompts for these images. Some didn't turn out so great, in my opinion. The examples are from mostly the first images generated for each prompt, at most I did two. It's fairly consistent, I think.
